Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.converters

Interface Summary
Converter<S> Able to convert values of a source type to one or more target types.
ConverterRegistry A registry for converters.
 

Class Summary
DefaultConverterRegistry A default converter registry implementation.
SimpleConverter<S,T> Abstract superclass for all converters that have both a single source type and a single target type.
 

Exception Summary
ConverterException Thrown by converter registries when no converter can be found or by converters in case of a conversion failure.
